subproject.description:
Output 1:  Demonstrated and practiced improvements in good governance, at national and municipal levels, for the three target groups – women, youth and children, in seven procedural areas – to ensure access to quality and appropriate service delivery 
Output 2:  Strengthened Capacities of Government Agencies and Thematic Civil Society Networks to effectively support good governance and dialogue initiatives and of Capacity Development Agents to support governance initiative working groups
Output 3: Increased Awareness of the Requirements and Results of Democratic Governance and Social Pressure for Good Governance
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Operationalizing Good Governan

title: Operationalizing Good Governance for Social Justice
